msgstr "显示用户偏好设置"

msgid "Which Zypper command enables parallel package downloads?"
msgstr "哪个 Zypper 命令可以启用并行软件包下载？"

msgid "zypper --fast"
msgstr "zypper --fast"

msgid "zypper -p"
msgstr "zypper -p"

msgid "The latest zypper uses parallel downloads by default"
msgstr "最新版 zypper 默认使用并行下载"

msgid "zypper turbo"
msgstr "zypper turbo"

msgid "Which file is the main configuration file for Zypper?"
msgstr "Zypper 的主配置文件是哪一个？"

msgid "/etc/zypp/zypp.conf"
msgstr "/etc/zypp/zypp.conf"

msgid "/etc/zypperrc"
msgstr "/etc/zypperrc"

msgid "/etc/package.conf"
msgstr "/etc/package.conf"

msgid "/usr/lib/zypper/config"
msgstr "/usr/lib/zypper/config"

msgid "Which of the following Zypper commands will clean all cached packages?"
msgstr "以下哪个 Zypper 命令会清理所有缓存的软件包？"

msgid "zypper refresh --clean"
msgstr "zypper refresh --clean"

msgid "zypper clean --all"
msgstr "zypper clean --all"

msgid "zypper purge-cache"
msgstr "zypper purge-cache"

msgid "zypper remove-cache"
msgstr "zypper remove-cache"

msgid "Zypper can install patterns. What is a pattern in Zypper terms?"
msgstr "Zypper 可以安装软件集。在 Zypper 术语中，软件集（pattern）是什么？"

msgid "A regex for matching package names"
msgstr "用于匹配软件包名称的正则表达式"

msgid "A group of packages defining a role or use-case"
msgstr "一组定义角色或用例的软件包"

msgid "A theming configuration file"
msgstr "一个主题配置文件"

msgid "A metadata tag for a repository"
msgstr "仓库的元数据标签"

msgid "What happens if you run 'zypper dup --from packman'?"
msgstr "如果运行 'zypper dup --from packman' 会发生什么？"

msgid "Only update the 'packman' repository metadata"
msgstr "仅更新 'packman' 软件源的元数据"

msgid "Remove all non-packman packages"
msgstr "移除所有非 packman 软件包"

msgid "Force upgrade of installed packages to versions from packman repository"
msgstr "强制将已安装的软件包升级到 packman 软件源中的版本"

msgid "Create a backup before upgrade"
msgstr "升级前创建备份"

msgid "Leap 16.0 improved repository management with CDN by default, RIS-managed repos, and fewer total repositories. How many distribution repos does Leap 16.0 include by default?"
msgstr "Leap 16.0 改进了软件源管理，默认使用 CDN、由 RIS 管理的软件源，并减少了软件源总数。Leap 16.0 默认包含多少个发行版软件源？"

msgid "14"
msgstr "14"

msgid "8"
msgstr "8"

msgid "6"
msgstr "6"

msgid "Leap 16.0 uses RIS-managed repos now. How do you tweak repo settings without breaking things?"
msgstr "Leap 16.0 现在使用 RIS 管理的软件源。如何在不影响正常运行的情况下调整软件源设置？"

msgid "/etc/zypp/repos.d/ like the good old days"
msgstr "/etc/zypp/repos.d/   如美好的旧时光"

msgid "Don’t touch distribution .repo files, they will get overwritten! Use /etc/zypp/vars.d instead."
msgstr "不要修改发行版的 .repo 文件，它们会被覆盖！请改用 /etc/zypp/vars.d。"

msgid "Run `zypper --edit-repo --force` — the official way."
msgstr "运行 `zypper --edit-repo --force` —— 官方方式。"

msgid "Edit repoindex.xml manually and cross your fingers."
msgstr "手动编辑 repoindex.xml，然后祈祷一切顺利。"

msgid "What can users do at software.opensuse.org?"
msgstr "用户可以在 software.opensuse.org 做什么？"

msgid "Install packages with zypper via a single click in the browser."
msgstr "在浏览器中单击即可使用 zypper 安装软件包。"

msgid "Browse and install additional software, including packages from home projects."
msgstr "浏览并安装更多软件，包括来自个人项目的软件包。"

msgid "View screenshots and details of cool open source software."
msgstr "查看优秀开源软件的截图和详细信息。"

msgid "All of the above."
msgstr "以上全部。"

msgid "At what manpage section would you look for zypper docs?"
msgstr "你会在哪个 manpage 章节查找 zypper 文档？"

msgid "What is yzpper?"
msgstr "yzpper 是什么？"

msgid "Turkish translation of zypper"
msgstr "zypper 的土耳其语翻译"

msgid "Reverse (undo) the last zypper command"
msgstr "反转（撤销）上一个 zypper 命令"

msgid "Symlink to zypper, to avoid error on keyboard with swapped Y and Z key [german]"
msgstr "指向 zypper 的符号链接，以避免在 Y 和 Z 键互换的键盘上出错 [德语]"

msgid "The project name of next gen zypper"
msgstr "下一代 zypper 的项目名称"

msgid "This one is tricky! We all know zypper rm --clean deps but what happens if you run `zypper rm --clean-deps rm`?"
msgstr "这个有点棘手！我们都知道 zypper rm --clean deps，但如果你运行 `zypper rm --clean-deps rm` 会发生什么？"

msgid "You uninstall the `rm` command and all its leftover dependencies. Good luck removing files afterward!"
msgstr "你卸载了 `rm` 命令及其所有残留依赖。祝你以后删除文件好运！"

msgid "Only the `rm` command gets removed, dependencies stay put."
msgstr "仅移除 `rm` 命令，依赖项保持不变。"

msgid "It cleans your system of the `rm` command but keeps a backup just in case."
msgstr "它会从你的系统中清除 `rm` 命令，但会保留一个备份以防万一。"

msgid "Nothing happens `rm` command belongs to coreutils."
msgstr "什么都不会发生，`rm` 命令属于 coreutils。"

msgid "Start Quiz"
msgstr "开始测验"

msgid "Start"
msgstr "开始"

msgid "Back"
msgstr "返回"

msgid "Submit"
msgstr "提交"

msgid "Next"
msgstr "下一步"

msgid "Quit"
msgstr "退出"

msgid "Submit and Quit"
msgstr "提交并退出"

msgid "Time left"
msgstr "剩余时间"

msgid "Score"
msgstr "分数"

msgid "Final"
msgstr "最终"

msgid "Restart"
msgstr "重新启动"

msgid "Question"
msgstr "问题"

msgid "Please enter a username to proceed."
msgstr "请输入用户名以继续。"

